## üöÄ Project Overview

**IPL Neon Auction** is a fully functional online auction system built with **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**, styled in **neon hacker / matrix theme**, supporting:

- Admin panel for auction management
- Bidder login & registration
- Live auction view for spectators
- Dynamic player bidding and history
- Firebase-ready integration for real-time updates

This project is suitable for **mock IPL auctions**, teaching real-time bidding systems, or as a showcase for neon-styled web interfaces.

---

## üé® Neon Hacker UI

- Dark / black background
- Neon green / cyan text glow
- Matrix-style animated background
- Responsive design with glowing buttons and panels
- Animated live bid updates

---

## üõ† Features

### 1Ô∏è‚É£ Admin Panel

- Login
- Start auction and load new players  
- Set base price and role for each player  
- Mark players as SOLD or UNSOLD  
- View current bid and history  

### 2Ô∏è‚É£ Bidder Panel

- Register new account  
- Login as bidder  
- Place bids on live auction players  
- Quick bid increments (+0.5, +1, +2 Cr)  
- View bid status and team info  

### 3Ô∏è‚É£ Viewer Panel

- Login as viewer (no bidding)  
- View current auction player  
- Watch live bid updates  
- Access full bid history  

### 4Ô∏è‚É£ Auction Mechanics

- Current bid display updates dynamically  
- Bid history logs team, time, and amount  
- Base price set by admin  
- Random next player generator for testing/demo  
- Neon glowing interface for immersive experience  

